  <p>Gets the value that is stored at <code>key</code> in <code>settings</code>.</p>  <p>A convenience variant of <link xref="Gio.Settings.get"/> for booleans.</p>  <p>It is a programmer error to give a <code>key</code> that isn't specified as
having a boolean type in the schema for <code>settings</code>.</p>
